node.text:
Our plans have changed, but our determination remains the same 🇺🇸 We might not be in Tokyo right now, but we will use this extra time to push ourselves to be citius, altius, fortius next year💪🏼

So grateful for this @poloralphlauren One-Year-Out Collection that supports @TeamUSA and helps us prepare to be our best 👊🏼

Check out the collection at the link in my bio ⭐️

node.text: Victoria gets REAL with me about her experience with binge eating, body image, and how being a college athlete can take a toll on your mental health. We talk about how she dealt with these challenges and her pathway to therapy and the help we all need from time to time. We end with some tips for performing under pressure, so you don’t want to miss that! My hope is that you all walk away with something that will help you improve your own mental health and remember you are NEVER alone!

node.title: Body Image, Mental Health & More with Victoria Garrick!

node.text: I had a little time on my hands today so I scrolled through my camera roll and threw together this video🤗 Grateful for all these times and these humans and can’t wait to make more memories! ❤️ @alixklineman @jenniferkessy & * @fiapogtenius we need some video with you! 🙈

Can always count on partner-to-coach @jenniferkessy for a balance of intensity and lightheartedness, to tell it like it is, and of course entertain us in the process 🤣 Grateful to have her on our team! 🙏🏼🙌🏼❤️ Enjoy this look at what goes on in our player box during a big match 👊🏼 (also don’t think my Gatorade matching my suit was a coincidence 💁🏼‍♀️) •••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••
Repost from @avpbeach

For the first time, we take you behind-the-scenes and in the coach's corner. Get an inside look at the coaching process and commentary of Olympic Silver Medalist and #AVP coach, @JenniferKessy, as she led the #ATeam into the Women's Final of the 2019 #AVPGoldSeries // Manhattan Beach Open.

SEMIS!!! Yesssss Al!! 👊🏼🙏🏼⚔️🇺🇸 @alixklineman ❤️

We have so much respect for that German 
team🤜🏼🤛🏼 I’ve played against Laura my entire career and she is SO good and such a gnarly competitor, and I’m so impressed with what Maggie has done in her short time on the beach, she’s playing so well🚀 Suffice it to say we are so grateful to pull out that W against them 🙌🏼

The legacy I want to leave behind is that I gave it everything that I have and that my mom would be proud. She’s why I am an advocate for those living with metastatic breast cancer today, and also why I am proud to be partnering with @verzenio, a treatment option for women living with HR+, HER2- MBC.

Information shared via direct or private message may be disclosed to Lilly and third parties in order to meet legal or regulatory requirements. #VerzenioPartner

A good win against a really good Cuban team we had never played before! I love battling out there alongside @alixklineman 🙌🏼🙏🏼⚔️ Grateful for another chance to compete, this time in the quarterfinals! Same time tomorrow against Germany! 👊🏼💪🏼🇺🇸

Thanks again for your positive vibes and cheering! 🥰🤗

node.text:
I wouldn’t be where I am today had it not been for the time I was able to spend with my mom, Margie. She’s who I am #RelentlessFor, and why time is so precious to me. And today with @verzenio, more time is possible for certain people living with HR+, HER2- metastatic breast cancer.

Verzenio was proven to help women with HR+, HER2- metastatic breast cancer live significantly longer. In a clinical study, women taking Verzenio + fulvestrant lived for a median of 46.7 months vs. 37.3 months on fulvestrant alone. In the same study, Verzenio + fulvestrant delayed cancer growth for a median of 16.4 months vs 9.3 months on fulvestrant alone.

Margie Ross was not a Verzenio patient. 

Information shared via direct or private message may be disclosed to Lilly and third parties in order to meet legal or regulatory requirements. #VerzenioPartner

node.text:
Say hello to @Tonal!🤗
Alix and I have been using Tonal for some of our strength training and it’s amazing. This was my first time ever lifting with digital weight🤯 and I was shocked at how efficient while challenging the workout was!💪🏼 I love that Tonal tracks my reps and volume, so I know exactly what I‘ve done after every training session. And the best part is it fits in my house!! 🤩 I can’t wait to keep using it to get stronger and to push myself with this new technology.👊🏼
#BeYourStrongest #PoweredByTonal #ATeam
